      <p>The <uicontrol>LIST PAGE BUSINESS LOGIC</uicontrol> tab enables you to configure business logic in  <ph href="../../../../Warehouse/Product_Name_Warehouse.xml#reference-9043/product_name"/> when you access the list page. It consists of only one event â€“ <uicontrol>Customize Toolbar</uicontrol>. For more information on this event, refer to <xref href="Customize_Toolbar.xml">Customize Toolbar Event</xref>. </p>
      <p>The blocks available  in the <uicontrol>LIST PAGE BUSINESS LOGIC</uicontrol> tab are similar to the <uicontrol>FORM BUSINESS LOGIC</uicontrol> tab except for the <uicontrol>ACTIONS</uicontrol> block. The <uicontrol>ACTIONS</uicontrol> block is the final output of the business logic that you
must configure once you navigate to the list page.</p>
      <p>The <uicontrol>LIST PAGE BUSINESS LOGIC</uicontrol> tab consists of the following blocks:</p>
